track_notes: Track start from Kintoki park near Kintoki Shrine. Very popular place of parking then better get reach early time in morning. Till Otome pass hard and rocky way but after Otome pass easy track to summits. Nice view of Mr Fuji from Otome pass.
Start Sengoku Bus stop and activate Kintokiyama KN-007 and Marudake KN-026 and decend to Kojiri pass.
